                {
                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p30z71h3w/manifest/annotation/p3",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">It is time however to finish the subject; it is extremely unpleasant\n                to<lb/> me, and no doubt equally so to you. However it is due to <add>?</add> to let\n                you<lb/> know how matters stand; and I believe I have a pretty accurate<lb/>\n                knowledge of all the main facts to form a correct opinion.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">On <date>Sunday</date> the ladies society had a meeting, and\n                requested<lb/> me to deliver another annual address. I believe I shall<lb/> comply,\n                let the result of the coming election be favourable or unfa<lb/>vourable.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Of the prayer book are now done</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(6)\">92 <add>?</add> of vol II</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(6)\">100 - - - III</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(6)\">42 - - IV</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(6)\">72 - - V</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(6)\">40 - - VI 352.</p>\n            <p>I hope confidently to be able to free<add>?</add> the 2nd vol. in about two<lb/>\n                weeks from today.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I believe <persName>Rachel</persName> enjoys herself very much;\n                but<lb/> occupation has prevented my seeing her yesterday &amp; today.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Give my best regards to <add>?</add><lb/>\n                <persName>Miss Judah</persName>\n                <persName>Mr. <add>?</add></persName>\n                <persName>Block</persName>, and cousin <persName>Ben</persName>.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">If you see the <persName>Ettings</persName> &amp;\n                    <persName>Cohens</persName>, especially <persName>Miss\n                    Reicha<add>?</add></persName><lb/> and <persName>Mrs. E. P. C.</persName> give\n                my remembrance to them</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">your obt nephew</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Isaac Leeser</persName>\n            </p>\n            "
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p30z71h3w/canvas/p3"
                }
              ]
            }
